Project

- Right click -> create -> 'Make Folder', 'Scripts', 'Scenes', 'Materials', 'Prefab'
- Right click -> show in explorer -> opens up file system location of folder
- Search form 
- Filter button
- Label button (ex audio, architecture, etc)
- Star button -> save search aka Fav
- Access to Asset Store when selected on fav search
- One Column vs Two Column View
- Zoom scale at the bottom

- Prefabs: are linked copies
- Update Prefabs by dragging and dropping GameObject on to Prefab
- Right click in Project -> create an empty prefab will be gray -> is empty
- Right click in hierarchy -> dragged into project will be blue -> has a transform

- F -> Focus
- Shift F = Edit -> Lock View to Selected -> Camera follows

